title: 2016 Norwegian First Division (women)
text:
The 2016 <a href="1.%20divisjon%20%28women%29">1. divisjon</a> was the second tier of <a href="Norway">Norwegian</a> women's <a href="association%20football">football</a> in 2016. The season kicked off on 16 April 2016, finishing on 6 November 2016.
The top placed team was be promoted to next year's <a href="Toppserien">Toppserien</a>. The second placed team contested a playoff against the 11th placed team from the <a href="2016%20Toppserien">2016 Toppserien</a> for the right to play in Toppserien next season.
